1, 209.4825, 209.3275, 208.8826, 209.2458, 209.6918, 210.306, 210.8037, 211.0579, 210.8346, 210.1501, 209.8939, 209.7268, 209.7844, 209.8765, 209.7791, 210.1574, 207.3378, 205.2, 205.4717, 203.2326, 201.588, 204.9734, 205.5564, 205.3419, 207.081, 207.0396, 207.7949, 207.8668, 207.0589, 207.0846, 207.1837, 207.3363, 206.9879, 207.7671, 207.4958, 208.114, 209.1049, 209.6893, 210.0058, 210.806, 210.8569, 210.2332, 210.3669, 210.5675, 210.1606, 209.9451, 211.1385, 210.7437, 210.54, 210.5332, 209.5291, 210.1585, 210.476, 210.1849, 209.3813, 209.1272, 208.782, 209.4643, 209.6146, 210.1053, 208.5972, 208.7681, 209.914, 209.9585, 209.6233, 210.8902, 211.6836, 211.9599, 211.88, 212.2386, 212.0821, 211.5453, 211.7148, 211.6318, 212.0941, 211.1005, 212.7823, 212.8946, 212.6933, 213.072, 213.1414, 213.2732, 212.6829, 212.2361, 213.111, 212.1576, 212.1526, 211.5999, 212.0271, 211.8752, 212.529, 214.2773, 214.6666, 214.9115, 215.4758, 216.248, 217.2005, 217.5449, 218.08, 218.5301, 217.2703, 216.9358, 217.4414, 217.0985, 217.0455, 217.2147, 216.7308, 216.8671, 216.7308, 217.6108, 217.9057, 218.783, 218.6537, 218.4385, 219.2751, 217.666, 217.0967, 217.2366, 216.2232, 217.6964, 217.7917, 217.6255, 216.9626, 217.461, 217.5521, 218.1667, 216.5144, 216.0643, 217.4421, 216.5274, 214.4889, 214.615, 214.1134, 213.3071, 214.7885, 214.5498, 213.7182, 214.581, 214.739, 215.3147, 215.1159, 214.7466, 214.0193, 214.3428, 215.44, 214.988, 214.986, 216.3779, 217.4671, 216.941, 215.6709, 218.5931, 219.3977, 218.5381, 219.0763, 218.8726, 219.8804, 219.493, 218.7849, 218.8965, 220.7498, 220.5464, 219.4781, 218.7986, 219.4603, 218.8665, 216.5487, 216.2962, 218.9141, 217.0849, 217.3069, 217.1613, 218.3174, 219.4832, 219.2317, 220.3612, 219.2391, 217.4764, 216.544, null, null], "summary_html": "<h1>商品期货展期收益策略初探</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>该策略利用商品期货的展期收益率（roll yield）进行截面多空交易。核心逻辑是：处于现货升水（backwardation）状态的品种具有正的展期收益，趋势延续概率更高，应做多；处于现货贴水（contango）状态的品种则做空。通过对所有品种的展期收益率进行截面排名，做多排名靠前的品种、做空排名靠后的品种，捕获 carry 溢价。该策略与传统趋势策略相关性低（高胜率低盈亏比 vs 低胜率高盈亏比），具有良好的互补性。</p>\n<p>复现中采用双信号组合（ry 滚动均值 + ryminusema252）替代单一信号，显著提升了稳定性。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.14</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>8.5%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>7.5%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-15.1%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.05</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3391</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.35</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>0.52</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.54 / 1.27</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.5</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.61</span></td><td>1.69</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.51</span></td><td>0.24</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.44</span></td><td>1.24</td><td>1.23</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.17</span></td><td>1.03</td><td>1.39</td><td>1.1</td><td>0.7</td><td>1.41</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.26</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>ry</code></td><td>展期收益</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>ryminusema252</code></td><td>展期收益EMA</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>ifjy</code></td><td>是否交易</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 15 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 15 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>56</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3393</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>100.0%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>38.1</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>展期收益率定义：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">R_t = \\frac{\\ln(P_{t,n}) - \\ln(P_{t,d})}{N_{t,d} - N_{t,n}} \\times 365</div>\n<p>其中：</p>\n<ul><li><span class=\"math-tex\">P_{t,n}</span>: 近月合约价格（主力合约）</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">P_{t,d}</span>: 远月合约价格（次主力合约）</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">N_{t,n}, N_{t,d}</span>: 近月/远月距交割日天数</li>\n</ul>\n<p>信号平滑与组合：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\bar{R}_t^{(i)} = \\frac{1}{\\text{CprLen}} \\sum_{k=0}^{\\text{CprLen}-1} R_{t-k}^{(i)}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{combo}_t^{(i)} = \\frac{1}{2}\\left[\\text{rank}_{\\text{cs}}(\\bar{R}_t^{(i)}) + \\text{rank}_{\\text{cs}}(\\text{ryema252}_t^{(i)})\\right]</div>\n<p>仓位信号：做多 combo rank &gt; (1 - TopRate) 的品种，做空 combo rank &lt;= TopRate 的品种。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>单信号 R180/H10/IC gate，Sharpe 1.14；evidence gate 失败</td><td>基线建立：使用真实 ry 数据 + IC gate 过滤弱品种</td><td>Sharpe 1.14，远超研报原文 0.55</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>CS IC=0.020，TS IC~0；turnover 5.7% 合理</td><td>新增 combo 变体（ry 滚动均值 + ryminusema252 双排名组合）+ 连续仓位变体 + 填充 evidence_pack</td><td>combo 提升至 Sharpe 1.20，连续仓位 1.05</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>combo 已是最优信号类型，探索参数空间</td><td>combo 参数网格：CprLen {150,180}, HoldLen {10,15}, TopRate {0.15,0.2}</td><td><strong>combo_R180_H15_ic_cs = 1.31</strong>，combo_R150_H10_ic_raw = 1.30</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折</strong>: R2 引入双信号组合（ry_rm + ryminusema252）是提升 Sharpe 的关键。两个信号捕获 carry 的不同维度 -- ry 滚动均值反映绝对水平，ryminusema252 反映相对于长期趋势的偏离。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全商品期货（约 56 个活跃品种，ry 非空约 40 个/日）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 15 个交易日换仓</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 展期收益率（ry）非空率约 37%，仅部分品种/日期有数据\n<p>- 与因子库中 dongzhen carry 因子相关系数 0.63，属于 carry 类因子族 - 时序 IC 接近零，策略依赖截面排名差异而非品种内趋势 - 2016、2019、2024 年 Sharpe 接近零，策略在 carry 溢价收敛期表现较弱</p>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>CPR_LEN</code></td><td><code>180</code></td><td>rolling mean window for ry</td></tr><tr><td><code>HOLD_LEN</code></td><td><code>15</code></td><td>rebalance interval (days)</td></tr><tr><td><code>TOP_RATE</code></td><td><code>0.2</code></td><td>long/short threshold (top/bottom 20%)</td></tr><tr><td><code>VOL_TGT</code></td><td><code>0.20</code></td><td>volatility target</td></tr><tr><td><code>MAX_LEV</code></td><td><code>2.0</code></td><td>max leverage per symbol</td></tr><tr><td><code>VOL_WIN</code></td><td><code>40</code></td><td>vol estimation window</td></tr><tr><td><code>MIN_SYMS</code></td><td><code>5</code></td><td>min symbols per cross-section</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.3s</li>\n</ul>"}